replies.body:
*gasps* senpai noticed meeeeee!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! {{summoner:31}} 
**coughs and regains composure**
I don't transcribe everything I hear, but honestly this piece impresses me so much because it's haunting, chaotic, and quite catchy. You've probably heard an overwhelming amount of feedback already, but I can't think of a better debut composition and I can't wait to see what else you've got for us!
